{
  "stem": "23428.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one day, in my block, the-- a Portuguese Jew stole shoes of somebody else and was caught.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was severely beaten by the blockalteste who was a French parliamentarian with whom, later, I became actually quite close, by name of Paul Self, who simply felt that one could not condone one prisoner stealing from another.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But this guy was terribly beaten.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So-- so you saw that sort of thing, but not from the SS, because the SS was not to be seen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I-- I would say, OK, the only time I remember seeing an SS man was when I was caught by him talking over the fence to the next rectangular camp, which was occupied by women.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in fact, there was a Hungarian woman, and I think all I was doing, in total innocence, is to-- is to practice my Hungarian with her.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, it was obviously not allowed to talk across this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the guy appeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was a steep slope before you got to the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was at the bottom of the slope.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The guy was on top.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so he called me to come up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And of course, I did this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In my best Prussian self, I stood absolutely immobile at attention while he ripped off some of the things that I had sewn on badly.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were exact regulations where your number had to be sewn and what not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
